::Prowl::

Prowl spins around as Shadow Wing lands near him. He looks calmly as her, 
nodding. "I might be a bit insane, yes. Me and Dinobot are going to rescue 
Iron Raptor and Tavatron. You go to the base and help defend it."

He frowns as he recieves Hot Rod's transmission. "No can do for now. Me and 
Dinobot will be back to finish off the preds later, WITH Iron Raptor and 
Tavatron. Untill then, I'm shutting off my comm."

He switches off that frequency, leaving his comm only open to Dinobot.
